Package stocker.model.general

Class FrameProfile

  • java.lang.Object
    • stocker.model.general.FrameProfileBase
      • stocker.model.general.FrameProfile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<FrameProfile>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FrameProfileChart
    public class FrameProfile
extends FrameProfileBase
    The frame profiles are used to contain data about all the different gui frames i.e. size, position. They are also used to determine if a frame is present or not.
    Author:
    Christoph Kaplan
